@startuml ClassDiagram_Proxy
title Class Diagram — Proxy (Caching) Pattern

skinparam classBackgroundColor White
skinparam classBorderColor DarkBlue
skinparam classArrowColor DarkBlue
skinparam stereotypeCBackgroundColor LightYellow
skinparam stereotypeIBackgroundColor LightBlue
skinparam noteBackgroundColor LightYellow
skinparam noteBorderColor DarkBlue

' ── Client ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

class FormMain {
    - r_FacebookService : IFacebookService
    --
    - loadAlbumsIntoGrid() : void
    - tryUploadPhotoToAlbum(i_Album : Album) : void
}
note top of FormMain : **Pattern role: Client**\nHolds only IFacebookService — unaware\nwhether it talks to Proxy or RealSubject.

' ── Subject (interface) ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────

interface IFacebookService {
    + LoggedInUser : User <<get>>
    + Login(i_AppId : string) : LoginResult
    + ConnectWithToken(i_Token : string) : LoginResult
    + Logout() : void
    + GetFriends() : List<User>
    + GetAlbums() : List<Album>
    + GetRecentPosts(i_MaxCount : int) : List<Post>
    + GetPhotosFromAlbum(i_Album : Album) : List<Photo>
    + PostStatus(i_Content : string) : void
    + UploadPhotoToAlbum(i_Album : Album, i_FilePath : string) : void
}
note top of IFacebookService : **Pattern role: Subject (interface)**\nShared by both Proxy and RealSubject,\nallowing the client to use either\ninterchangeably.

' ── Proxy ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

class CachingFacebookProxy {
    - r_RealService : IFacebookService
    - m_CachedFriends : List<User>
    - m_CachedAlbums : List<Album>
    - m_CachedPosts : List<Post>
    - m_CachedPostsMaxCount : int
    - r_CachedAlbumPhotos : Dictionary<string, List<Photo>>
    --
    + GetFriends() : List<User>
    + GetAlbums() : List<Album>
    + GetRecentPosts(i_MaxCount : int) : List<Post>
    + GetPhotosFromAlbum(i_Album : Album) : List<Photo>
    + PostStatus(i_Content : string) : void
    + UploadPhotoToAlbum(i_Album : Album, i_FilePath : string) : void
    + InvalidateCache() : void
}
note right of CachingFacebookProxy : **Pattern role: Proxy**\nIntercepts calls to the RealSubject.\nReturns cached result on hit;\ndelegates to RealSubject on miss.\nInvalidates cache on write operations.

' ── Real Subject ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

class FacebookManager {
    - m_LoginResult : LoginResult
    --
    + GetFriends() : List<User>
    + GetAlbums() : List<Album>
    + GetRecentPosts(i_MaxCount : int) : List<Post>
    + GetPhotosFromAlbum(i_Album : Album) : List<Photo>
    + PostStatus(i_Content : string) : void
    + UploadPhotoToAlbum(i_Album : Album, i_FilePath : string) : void
}
note right of FacebookManager : **Pattern role: RealSubject**\nThe actual implementation that\nperforms the Facebook API calls.\nWrapped by the Proxy.

' ── Relationships ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

FormMain "1" ..> "1" IFacebookService : <<uses>>

CachingFacebookProxy ..|> IFacebookService
FacebookManager ..|> IFacebookService

CachingFacebookProxy "1" *-- "1" FacebookManager : r_RealService

@enduml
